title: Data Security And Legal Compliance In The Technology Industry
combined_text: Data Security And Legal Compliance In The Technology Industry. mondaq.com.
summary: Technology companies must prioritize robust data security measures to protect sensitive information. Simultaneously, strict adherence to evolving legal compliance requirements is essential for avoiding penalties and maintaining trust.

title: Snowflake acquires Crunchy Data for enterprise - grade PostgreSQL to counter Databrick Neon buy
combined_text: Snowflake acquires Crunchy Data for enterprise - grade PostgreSQL to counter Databrick Neon buy. infoworld.com.
summary: Snowflake acquired Crunchy Data to enhance its enterprise-grade PostgreSQL capabilities. This acquisition is seen as a response to Databricks' purchase of Neon, signaling a growing competition in the data platform market.

title: Space Force And NGA Delineate Commercial Data - Buying Roles
combined_text: Space Force And NGA Delineate Commercial Data - Buying Roles. aviationweek.com.
summary: The Space Force will focus on acquiring commercial satellite data for tactical applications. The National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA) will continue leading the acquisition of commercial geospatial data for strategic intelligence purposes.
